&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Result&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://yudo-homepage.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/prod/prod/successcase/20220331184423528c64f9-93c3-4d0a-b816-5a568ac22b76.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 1031px; height: 722px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#bb1e4d;&quot;&gt;Remove the pressure molding step&lt;/span&gt; by post-foaming the core layer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;In order to increase the filling rate and foaming effect of the core layer, the filling is performed by controlling the injection speed of the main screw (the internal pressure of the product is lower than that of pressure molding, so the post-foaming proceeds smoothly)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;Weight loss of approximately &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#bb1e4d;&quot;&gt;6%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;(Previous sample: 205g / Solution applied sample: 193g)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;Increased cushioning effect and elasticity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

